title: Terrorizer - January 2016
description:
English | 84 pages | PDF | 77.7 MB





Terrorizer is the world's most authoritative extreme music magazine and when it comes to heavy metal and all forms of an ungodly racket, hell, it's the best friend you'll ever have. Since its first outing in 1993, Terrorizer has put out over 200 issues jam packed with the most brutal new extreme music on the planet every single month. Take a look at the bands on our cover for an idea and remember that Terrorizer pioneered forms of music and covered artists that no-one else would touch, name it and we were probably there first! If you're a real metal or hardcore fan, you really should be reading Terrorizer
